    <content>&lt;p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;Your task in this module is to&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;assess&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;how the adult learners&amp;nbsp;in your classroom currently&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;experience agency&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;and to develop learners&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;'&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;&amp;nbsp;self-advocacy skills for use in the workplace.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;Developing adult learners&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;'&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;&amp;nbsp;sense of agency and ownership of learning is a key goal of&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;andragogy,&amp;nbsp;or the practice of teaching adults.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;&lt;img src="@@PLUGINFILE@@/Divider%20Wave%20%281%29.png?time=1674934808042" alt="" width="1920" height="195" role="presentation" class="img-responsive atto_image_button_text-bottom"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</content>
